725885f-a.title: Queens: 147th Street - 37th Avenue
725885f-a.text:
147th Street, east side, opposite Thirty-seventh Ave. If Thirty-
seventh Ave. is extended on its present line, this house would be at
the S.E. corner of the above mentionedstreet. This view shows the
home of William Barclay Parsons in 1925.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster.
